Class JarStreamModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream

              • com.ibm.wala.classLoader.JarStreamModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class JarStreamModule
extends java.util.jar.JarInputStream
implements Module
    Read in a jar file from an input stream. Most parts are copied from the NestedJarFileModule class and adapted to work with an input stream.
    Author:
    Juergen Graf <juergen.graf@gmail.com>
